<body>
  <div class="inputContainer position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle">
    <h1 class="setHeadling">國立高雄大學學生住宿系統</h1>
    <form method='post' action='/forgotPassword'>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="UID" id="inputAccount" placeholder="請輸入帳號" style="margin-top: 15px;">
      </div>
        <input type="submit" class="submitButton" value="送出" id="Submit" onclick=showMessage()>
    </form>
    <p id="mailMessage" class="setMessage" style="display: none;">已發送重設密碼連結至您的信箱，請於十分鐘內查看並重設密碼！</p>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
